       Black Aracnia looked deep into Quickstrikes eyes. He was still so 
confused, so disoriented. He was often groggy like this, "shh, everything is 
ok. And soon, we wont have to worry about the other Predacons, that is if our 
plan follows through."
       Turning, she looked to the offspring. What could she do with her? What 
were her talents? If she would only talk with her mother...
